Package: correlateR
Type: Package
Title: Fast correlations and covariances.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-07-24
Author: Anders Ellern Bilgrau
Maintainer: Anders Ellern Bilgrau <anders.ellern.bilgrau@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/AEBilgrau/correlateR
BugReports: https://github.com/AEBilgrau/correlateR/issues/new
Description: Fast, robust, and efficient estimation of marginal, partial, and
    semi-partial (part) correlations and covariances.
License: GPL (>=2)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.10.6),
    GMCM
Depends:
    RcppEigen
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppEigen
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 0.3)
Enhances: microbenchmark
